<item>
            <title>[MCHECKSTYLE-302] Using inline configuration does not work with Maven 2.2.1</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MCHECKSTYLE-302</link>
                <project id="12317223" key="MCHECKSTYLE">Maven Checkstyle Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A test project is already checked in, as part of the IT for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MCHECKSTYLE-295&quot; title=&quot;Test resources are not included&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MCHECKSTYLE-295&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MCHECKSTYLE-295&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. That IT will fail with Maven 2.2.1 complaining that the attribute &quot;name&quot; is missing from element &quot;module&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
